       <p>As an assignment for our syllabi we were asked to implement a project using Mongodb and php. Our group of 4 students chose to implement Library Management System.In this each student has a unique user id and password using which </p>

	<p>Student can access the following information:</p>
	<ol>
		<li>Available books and their current copies.
		<li>Number of books issued to him.
		<li>Date of Issue and Return.
		<li>Due Fine.
		<li>Upcoming books.
	</ol>
	Admin can access the following information:
	<ol>
		<li>Available books and their current copies.
		<li>Total Number of books issued and the user to whom it has been issued.
		<li>Dates of Issue and Return.
		<li>Due Fine.
		<li>Upcoming books.
		<li>Authority to add the book to the exisiting copies, once it has been issued.
	</ol>

